        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Crafted from black iron, this crude suit of +2 resilient full plate is designed to make you look like a horned demon, with your face peering out of the screaming maw of the beast.</p>\n<p>While wearing the armor, you can attack with the helmet's horns. They are a martial melee weapon with the effects of a <em>+2 weapon potency rune</em>. They deal 2d8 piercing damage and have the deadly d12 trait. On a critical hit with the horns, the target must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:30] against the Abyssal plague disease. The horns can't be etched with any runes.</p>\n<p>If you aren't evil, you're @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} and can't recover from this condition while wearing <em>demon armor</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span> Command</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dimension Door]</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You are evil; supply one casting of <em>dimension door</em>.</p>"
